headline: J.P. Morgan Advises Playing the Lower Interest Rates Theme With These 2 Food Stocks
summary: Friday’s markets got a jolt of optimism when Federal Reserve Chair Jerome Powell, speaking at the Jackson Hole symposium, dropped what might be the week’s most market-friendly hint. A possible interest-rate cut could be on the table as soon as September, particularly if signs of a cooling job market continue to mount.
